25
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,270
Well, I will

26
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:30,460
go out first.

27
00:02:30,580 --> 00:02:32,110
Call me if you need anything.

28
00:02:33,580 --> 00:02:35,700
Well, I'll shower first.

29
00:02:37,270 --> 00:02:37,900
Okay.

30
00:02:41,020 --> 00:02:41,700
I...

31
