Jing Xichi.

35
00:03:21,830 --> 00:03:23,830
I can't sleep.

36
00:03:24,460 --> 00:03:25,110
Is

37
00:03:25,110 --> 00:03:26,300
my typing noise too loud

38
00:03:26,355 --> 00:03:27,180
and bothering you?

39
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:28,460
No.

40
00:03:29,070 --> 00:03:30,830
I think I have got used
to my own bed.

41
00:03:37,140 --> 00:03:38,860
When I couldn't sleep,

42
00:03:39,230 --> 00:03:40,580
I used to think

43
00:03:40,888 --> 00:03:42,300
of something happy and relaxing,

44
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,270
and then I'd fall asleep.

45
00:03:45,460 --> 00:03:46,230
Did it work?

46
00:03:47,950 --> 00:03:49,460
It worked for me.

47
00:03:52,950 --> 00:03:54,230
What should I think about?

48
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:56,830
Do you want

49
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:58,390
to think

50
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:01,230
about what our home

51
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:03,580
will be like in the future?

52
00:04:05,740 --> 00:04:07,270
Our home?

53
00:04:15,580 --> 00:04:17,910
I'd like to have lots
and lots of pictures,

54
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,910
all over the wall.

55
00:04:22,060 --> 00:04:23,030
Pictures of us

56
00:04:23,844 --> 00:04:25,555
in the family housing compound,

57
00:04:27,150 --> 00:04:28,260
pictures of us now,

58
00:04:29,940 --> 00:04:30,860
and

59
00:04:32,260 --> 00:04:33,590
pictures of us when we're old.

60
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,230
It hurts.

61
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:37,030
