00:38:03,910 --> 00:38:04,950
Time of death,

865
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:06,140
20:37.

866
00:38:07,022 --> 00:38:08,955
Take the family
to get a death certificate.

867
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:10,540
Remember to calm the family down.

868
00:39:42,620 --> 00:39:43,100
Who's it?

869
00:39:43,540 --> 00:39:45,177
Your food delivery has arrived.

870
00:39:47,700 --> 00:39:48,020
What?

871
00:39:50,288 --> 00:39:51,377
I didn't order any food.

872
00:39:51,422 --> 00:39:52,350
It's not my name.

873
00:39:55,990 --> 00:39:56,620
I ordered it.

874
00:39:59,020 --> 00:39:59,830
Thank you.

875
00:40:04,910 --> 00:40:05,500
Have you eaten?

876
00:40:11,060 --> 00:40:11,620
Thank you.

877
00:40:16,990 --> 00:40:17,500
Just eat.

878
00:40:17,700 --> 00:40:18,020
Okay.

879
00:40:39,100 --> 00:40:41,100
Your house has
the same floor plan as mine.

880
00:40:41,910 --> 00:40:43,333
How much did you rent it for?

881
00:40:45,750 --> 00:40:46,390
2,500 yuan.

882
00:40:47,180 --> 00:40:47,470
What?

883
00:40:48,430 --> 00:40:49,140
2,500 yuan.

884
00:40:49,844 --> 00:40:50,540
What about you?

885
00:40:51,310 --> 00:40:51,950
3,000 yuan.

886
00:40:53,950 --> 00:40:55,350
The landlord told me

887
00:40:55,790 --> 00:40:56,950
I got a great deal,

888
00:40:57,488 --> 00:41:00,133
saying it was the lowest price
in the neighborhood.

889
00:41:00,244 --> 00:41:02,577
It turns out
that a top student gets tricked too.

890
00:41:24,870 --> 00:41:26,700
I've actually imagined countless times

891
00:41:28,700 --> 00:41:29,470
a patient dying

892
00:41:29,500 --> 00:41:30,470
in front of me.

893
00:41:33,430 --> 00:41:35,060
I thought I was ready for it.

894
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:39,830
But when it came to that moment,

895
00:41:42,470 --> 00:41:44,180
I realized I had overestimated myself.

896
00:42:10,790 --> 00:42:11,620
Maybe

897
00:42:13,180 --> 00:42:14,540
one day you'll get used to it.

898
00:42:18,180 --> 00:42:20,020
Get used to facing death?

899
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:27,060
Get used to accepting

900
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:28,555
the cycle of life more openly

901
00:42:29,950 --> 00:42:32,220
and face up to your responsibilities
as a doctor.

902
00:44:22,721 --> 00:44:27,891
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

903
00:44:29,681 --> 00:44:34,761
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

904
00:44:36,531 --> 00:44:41,881
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

905
00:44:42,191 --> 00:44:47,681
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

906
00:44:50,271 --> 00:44:55,291
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

907
00:44:57,081 --> 00:45:02,321
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

908
00:45:03,921 --> 00:45:09,341
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

909
00:45:09,801 --> 00:45:15,301
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

910
00:45:16,501 --> 00:45:20,461
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

911
00:45:20,461 --> 00:45:25,451
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

912
00:45:25,581 --> 00:45:29,011
♪And full of life♪

913
00:45:30,301 --> 00:45:33,761
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

914
00:45:33,761 --> 00:45:38,871
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

915
00:45:39,131 --> 00:45:43,521
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

916
00:45:44,021 --> 00:45:47,921
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

917
00:45:47,921 --> 00:45:52,861
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

918
00:45:52,861 --> 00:45:55,651
♪To know right from wrong♪

919
00:45:57,561 --> 00:46:01,091
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

920
00:46:01,091 --> 00:46:04,341
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

921
00:46:04,501 --> 00:46:10,261
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

922
00:46:10,681 --> 00:46:15,281
♪At just the right time♪

